The following files need to be updated when the hostname,PATH and URL changes.....

Look for the string - "window.location.replace" to locate those lines and change as required:

~/src/views/tasks/js_insert_task.php
~/src/views/tasks/upd_view.php
~/src/views/tasks/js_insert_root_task.php


Also, look for the string - "window.open" and update the URL of the below file:

~/src/views/projects/index.php
